channel.title: Best way to level
channel.description:
Ello. At the moment im 40 attack, 59 strength, 40 def, 57 range, 60 mage. Id like to get 70 strength and range. The only problem is, i duno where to train. I autoed at PC and was getting 100 zeal in an hour and a half, and around 15k strength xp, so in total around 35k xp in an hour and a half. I haven't tried Soul Wars, but i figure at my level i won't be getting much xp during the game, and would get like 8k every 20 mins. (Maybe more or less, i don't know.)
So in short question 1: Do i train strength at PC or soul wars?
Question 2: Should i train range at PC or SoulWars, or at rock crabs with a cannon and steel knives.
